<TITLE> Laksmi Puja Saturday </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Oct 2 (bdnews24.com)The Hindu community will observe Laksmi Puja to worship the goddess of wealth, on Saturday. Laksmi Puja takes place on the full moon after the end of Durga Puja, when the devotees perform rituals expecting the betterment to their livelihood. Temples in Dhaka and throughout the country will also hold the Puja rituals beside those at the houses.
